{"tid":968451,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"[絕技╴絲打入] 傳授絲打屙M大法","createTime":"2019-01-04T08:49:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-04T10:17:53.000Z","uid":135160,"like":10,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"bbf638792a29de36e94a8ab4845cc34817254139","tid":968451,"uid":135160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T08:49:38.000Z","msg":"相信冇邊個絲打會鍾意黎M <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n正所謂獨樂樂不如眾樂樂 <br />\n所以我特意傳授絲打屙M大法,黎縮短黎M嘅時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n一般每次黎M都會維持一星期左右 <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nDAY1 少量M <br />\nDAY2-3大量M <br />\n啲M真係有如滔滔江水,連綿不絕 <br />\n基本上一個鐘要換一次M巾<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n訓覺唔用40CM特長M巾 一定會溜M <br />\n到時又要洗底褲同換床單<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nDAY4 正常流量 <br />\nDAY5-7 埋尾 ,驟M <br />\n<br />\n正常黎講,每次經期子宮內膜嘅血量都差唔,大約50毫升 <br />\n屙M大法嘅理念就係,盡量將M喺第一至第二日逼出 <br />\n縮短高峰期,減少經期間不適及不便 <br />\n第3日或之後嘅M 就只會係好少量,已經可以用護墊,唔會阻礙日常生活 <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n方法如下<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f77cc4364ed5fc704afa838477f7801e98ddd7ba","tid":968451,"uid":135160,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T08:51:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b81462f82486aabca44b2a72f7614e3f279b6329","tid":968451,"uid":29929,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T08:53:28.000Z","msg":"幫你授精咪有十個月無M到囉<br />\n<br />\n持續受精連屙M都慳番"},{"pid":"e114ac60f5feaaab0d06fdadfaae8b111eea656e","tid":968451,"uid":42426,"like":1,"di